				<h1>The Best (Old) Books We Read in 2024</h1>
		<h2>Because If You Only Read What Everyone Else is Reading...</h2>
    <div class="inner">
		<div class="post_header_wrapper">
    				</div>
				<div class="author_info" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
			<div class="author_name">By&nbsp;<a href="https://lithub.com/author/emily-temple/" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">Emily&nbsp;Temple</span></a></div>
			<div class="author_hr"><hr/></div>
			<div class="publish_date">December 24, 2024</div>
		</div>
		<div class="social_links">
						<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?via=lithub&text=The+Best+%28Old%29+Books+We+Read+in+2024&url=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fthe-best-old-books-we-read-in-2024%2F"><span class="social_twitter"></span></a>
			<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fthe-best-old-books-we-read-in-2024%2F&t=The+Best+%28Old%29+Books+We+Read+in+2024"><span class="social_facebook"></span></a>
